WEBVTT

00:00.254 --> 00:01.821
<i>Amy:</i>
<i>Previously on "Heartland":</i>

00:01.888 --> 00:03.454
Jake: You know, he's only
hanging out with you

00:03.456 --> 00:05.125
'cause he thought your dad was
gonna be here tonight, right -

00:05.192 --> 00:06.326
<i>'cause of his demo.</i>

00:06.393 --> 00:08.128
You don't anything
about that.

00:08.195 --> 00:10.130
I don't want you
to get hurt.

00:10.347 --> 00:13.682
I can take care of myself,
thank you.

00:13.750 --> 00:15.584
I've made a decision.

00:15.652 --> 00:18.086
I want you and Peter
to have the Hanley farm.

00:18.154 --> 00:20.822
Is this what you want?

00:20.890 --> 00:21.591
(Sighs)

00:21.890 --> 00:22.591
Yes.

00:22.659 --> 00:24.526
It doesn't matter whether Miranda's
a good mother or not;

00:24.594 --> 00:28.129
Ninety percent of all cases
are awarded to the mother -

00:28.197 --> 00:29.963
as if a guy can't even be
a good caregiver.

00:30.031 --> 00:31.865
Well, your history
speaks to that.

00:31.933 --> 00:33.334
I thought you wanted
to marry me

00:33.402 --> 00:34.802
because you loved me,

00:34.869 --> 00:37.869
not because you were trying
to win some custody battle.

